    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for solid, dependable transportation at an honest price? This fair-condition vehicle gets the job done! It shows its age with some visible wear on the interior and exterior \u2014 you'll notice the signs of real-world use \u2014 but it runs and drives, making it a practical choice for everyday needs. No frills, no surprises \u2014 just a straightforward, functional car at a price that reflects exactly what it is. Great for commuters or anyone who needs reliable wheels without breaking the bank!",
