    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and that is a completely honest and accurate representation \u2014 this car is as close to perfect as you will find on the used market. The exterior is genuinely flawless, with no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections of any kind; it looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally impressive, with no wear on the seats, carpets, or trim, and all controls, features, and electronics functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with all maintenance up to date and no mechanical issues to report. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that truly lives up to the mint label \u2014 you will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Pristine & Picture-Perfect \u2014 A Truly Exceptional Find! \ud83c\udf1f This vehicle is in genuine mint condition, and it shows in every detail! The exterior is flawless \u2014 gleaming paint, no scratches, dents, or blemishes to speak of. Step inside and you'll find an immaculate interior that looks and smells fresh, with zero signs of wear. Every system runs beautifully, and the car drives as smoothly as the day it left the lot. If you've been searching for a vehicle that feels truly like-new without the new-car price tag, this is it. Don't miss your chance to own something this special! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, functional vehicle at a down-to-earth price? This car is honestly priced and ready to get you where you need to go! It shows its age and use \u2014 you'll notice some cosmetic wear and a few imperfections that come with real-world driving \u2014 but it remains a dependable option for buyers who want practical transportation without breaking the bank. The mechanicals are functional, and with a little TLC, this could be a great everyday driver or a rewarding project car. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, and buyers can expect a reliable, well-maintained used vehicle that performs well in daily driving. The exterior shows some minor signs of normal wear \u2014 small scratches or light scuffs consistent with regular use \u2014 but overall presents quite well. The interior is clean and functional, with no major damage to the seats, trim, or dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has been kept up with routine maintenance. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and air conditioning \u2014 are in proper working order. This is a solid everyday driver that offers good value without the premium price tag of a mint-condition vehicle. Buyers should expect a dependable car that is ready to go, with the minor cosmetic imperfections typical of a used vehicle at this price point.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "terse_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "terse_7",
      "description": "A reliable used car in good condition with minor cosmetic blemishes and solid mechanical performance.",
